text: Victoria Bush (born 15 January 1978) is an English actress and comedian. She is best known for portraying the roles of Tina O'Kane in the ITV prison-based drama series Bad Girls (2001–2006), and Sonya Donnegan in the BBC school-based drama series Waterloo Road (2012–2015).
